snippet.title: Amber Heard ''Hot Mess'' [Merry Christmas Steven]
snippet.description:
SONG; Cobra Starship ''Hot Mess''
^ Hope it's not blocked *cringeee*

FANDOM; Amber Heard In;
Syrup, The Rum Diaries, All The Boys Love Mandy Lane, 3 Days To Kill, The Stepfather, The Informers, Drive Angry, Machete Kills, Never Back Down, Paranoia, The Playboy Club
& Various photoshoots; Malibu Magazine, Guess Jeans - Fall 2011 Campaign, Fashions April 2010 cover shoot , Nylon TV, 

COLORING;
SilverBeautyxvideos

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To Most Awesome Guy In Germany...
and probably most of the world (Not all..because i have a dad and a brother) LOL 
Steveeeeeey! (CrazyStev0)

http://www.youtube.com/user/CrazyStev0
http://www.youtube.com/user/CrazyStev0
http://www.youtube.com/user/CrazyStev0

So i ooohed and ahhhed over you're video.
i planned it, started it, deleted it, re-done, deleted....Then BOOM
It hit me.
The song was totally out of the blue so i hope you like it?
My original idea was a Amber heard ''Mandy Lane'' and Dexter thing but my inspiration totally buzzed out on that i'm afraid....it was very hard to mask!
I hope my tribute to Amber for you was a good enough gift though?

MERRY CHRISTMAS & A HAPPY NEW YEAR!

I hope you have a wonderful Christmas :)
Love you longtime!!!
Amy 

P.s. Sorry for the quality in some clips.
YouTube isn't always the best clip source!
---------------------------------------------------------------

For anyone who is not Steven...
MERRY CHRISTMAS & A HAPPY NEW YEAR!
Love me :)
